headline-user:
Ingénieur en génie minéral de formation, je me distingue par mon
dynamisme et ma capacité à piloter avec succès les opérations des mines à
ciel ouvert. Ma motivation est sans cesse alimentée par la recherche de
nouveaux défis au sein de l'industrie extractive.

I will facilitate partnerships between ZVENIA and key stakeholders, organize knowledge-sharing events, and promote the platform’s services among professionals and institutions. By ensuring strong visibility and engagement in the mining community, I will help drive membership growth, knowledge exchange in ZVENIA’s plateform.

headline-user: As a Mining Production Engineer, I am responsible for overseeing and optimizing daily mining operations to achieve safe, efficient, and cost-effective production. My role involves coordinating drilling, blasting, loading, and hauling activities, ensuring that production targets are consistently met.
why_do_you_want: I want to be a ZVENIA Country Manager because I am passionate about advancing the mining industry through knowledge sharing, collaboration, and professional development. This role will allow me to connect mining professionals in my country, bridge knowledge gaps, and create opportunities that elevate both individuals and the industry as a whole.
how_can_you_contribute: I can contribute by leveraging my experience in open-pit mining operations, production leadership, and professional networking to grow ZVENIA’s presence in my country. I will actively promote the platform, create partnerships, and share practical insights from the field. Through mentorship, events, and knowledge exchange, I will help expand ZVENIA’s community and strengthen its impact on mining professionals.

headline-user: Mining professional with proven expertise in Life of Mine (LOM) strategy. Skilled in leading technical services teams, mentoring, and driving operational excellence through safe, compliant, and cost-efficient practices. Experienced in mine design, scheduling, drill & blast operations.
why_do_you_want: I would like to become a ZVENIA Promoter because I am passionate about advancing the mining industry through knowledge sharing, collaboration, and innovation. With my background in mine planning, design, and operational optimisation, I see this platform as an excellent opportunity to contribute valuable insights while also learning from peers across the sector.
how_can_you_contribute: Being part of ZVENIA will allow me to expand my professional network, connect with experts across different disciplines, and stay at the forefront of emerging trends and technologies in mining. I am particularly motivated by the chance to influence discussions that shape the industry’s future, while also strengthening my visibility and thought leadership within the mining community.

headline-user:
Connecting top talent with impactful mining careers — that's been my mission for as long as I can remember. 

For over a decade, I've been passionately connecting skilled professionals with rewarding careers in the mining sector.
why_do_you_want: I want to be a ZVENIA Promoter because I believe in the brand’s vision of empowering individuals to achieve their goals of influencing the industry, sharing insights and shaping the future of mining. With my extensive experience in recruitment, marketing, and building professional networks, I am confident I can effectively promote ZVENIA’s products and values. I am excited to leverage my skills to attract new audiences, drive engagement, and contribute to ZVENIA’s growth and success.
how_can_you_contribute: I can contribute to ZVENIA’s growth through my 13 years of mining industry recruitment experience, content writing, sharing insights, writing long-form articles, and conducting research and studies. By creating engaging, industry-relevant content and leveraging my expertise, I can attract and educate new audiences. My research and analysis skills will support data-driven strategies, while thought leadership articles and insights will enhance ZVENIA’s credibility and visibility.

headline-user: A professional mining engineer with good experience in open pit mining operations and planning as well as technical and feasibility studies of mining projects. Have master degree of mining engineering (geomechanics) from the Bandung Institute of Technology
why_do_you_want: I see the role as an excellent opportunity for mutual growth. I believe that my experience in the mining field will be a valuable asset in promoting ZVENIA's platform. In return, I am excited to gain increased visibility and networking opportunities within the professional community that ZVENIA serves.
how_can_you_contribute: My contribution would be a strategic one, focusing on building a stronger, more engaged community around ZVENIA. I can help identify and engage with key stakeholders, attract new users, and act as a representative and advocate for the platform's mission. By highlighting ZVENIA's unique features and benefits, I can help drive organic growth and solidify its position as a leading resource for the mining industry.

headline-user: I am a Geology graduate from the Federal University of Oye Ekiti, passionate about understanding the Earth’s structure and processes. I gained practical experience at Norike Geotech Limited, conducting soil tests and investigations, and currently work with AOA Geo-net Limited to advance my expertise
why_do_you_want: I want to be a ZVENIA Promoter because I’m passionate about contributing to the growth and innovation of the mining sector. As someone actively engaged in geosciences, I see ZVENIA as a unique platform to connect with like-minded professionals, share valuable knowledge, and help bridge gaps within the mining community. I’m excited by the opportunity to promote meaningful conversations, support emerging trends, and amplify voices that can shape the future of sustainable mining practices.
how_can_you_contribute: I can contribute to ZVENIA’s growth by actively promoting the platform within my academic and professional circles, especially among students, researchers, and early-career geoscientists who are often seeking specialized communities to grow in. With my background in geology and interest in mining, I can help spark meaningful discussions, share valuable insights from both academic and field experiences, and encourage knowledge exchange.

why_do_you_want: As a ventilation engineer in the mining industry, I understand the critical importance of knowledge sharing and innovation in ensuring safety, efficiency, and sustainability underground. This is why I am eager to become a ZVENIA Promoter. ZVENIA offers a powerful platform where professionals like me can contribute to a broader dialogue on mining best practices, particularly in specialized areas like mine Ventilation. I want to use this opportunity to grow my professional network.
how_can_you_contribute: As a ventilation engineer, I can contribute by sharing insights on underground airflow design, safety protocols, gas monitoring, and energy efficiency. I aim to highlight real-world ventilation challenges and solutions, helping others understand its vital role in safe, productive mining.

how_can_you_contribute: I bring extensive experience building partnerships with local mining firms, regulators and communities — helping unlock projects, streamline operations, and scale new technology adoption. I will localize ZVENIA’s offerings to address specific challenges (e.g. safety, environment, labor), expand the customer base through targeted outreach, deliver strong financial results, and embed high quality standards to deepen trust and reputation in the region.

why_do_you_want: want to be a ZVENIA Promoter because I am very interested in the mining industry. I enjoy learning and sharing useful information with others. I have experience working in the petrochemical field, and now I study mining engineering. I believe this is a good chance to meet new people, grow my knowledge, and help others in the mining field. I want to support the ZVENIA community and be part of its growth.
how_can_you_contribute: I can contribute to ZVENIA’s growth by sharing useful posts, videos, and ideas about mining and petrochemical work on platforms like LinkedIn. I will talk about important topics, safety, and new technologies in the mining industry. I can help more people learn about ZVENIA, invite others to join, and build strong connections. With my background in petrochemicals and my current mining engineering studies, I can bring real knowledge and experience to the community.
product_description_zads: We share educational content, technical knowledge, and visual materials related to the mining and petrochemical industries. Our goal is to connect professionals, students, and experts through clear and helpful posts, videos, and blog articles.
